room_title: Escape room "The Clue" by Great Escape Lakeside in Orlando
room_description: To begin the game, you'll "lock" yourselves inside the Clue bedroom/bathroom wing and will only be able to exit when you've solved all of the mysteries, puzzles, and you've figured out the final code to open the doors. As in the popular board game "CLUE," the objective is to find out which character committed murder, with which weapon, and in which room of the Clue Mansion.
